descript.abstract: Data set was initially created by Miller Management. It was maintained by the Story County Planning and Zoning office until May 2004 for the purposes of maintaining an E911 map. Since May 2004 it has been maintained by the Story County Auditor's Office.
descript.purpose: The purpose of this data is to maintain an accurate centerline file for various purposes (general county maps, geocoding, emergency response).

citeinfo.origin: Miller Management for Story County Planning and Zoning

idinfo.useconst: This feature class is not intended to be an exact account of the actual physical location of the roads represented. It is only to be used as an indication of the general location of the roads.
idinfo.accconst: Digital and hard copy maps are available upon request for a fee (based on Story County MAPS policies).
